channel.description: Hi............................................................................................ I am trying to add the original PI teleports to my server because the source I am using had different teleports.. So what I am trying to do is make it like the "Monster teleport" Has like 4 or 5 different monsters to tele to. I added in playerassistant.java the "Monster teleport" and "Boss teleport" and all that. And in clickingbuttons.java I added the options in it like in Monster teleport it would say "Rock crabs" and the other stuff and I also added in clickingbuttons.java so that when you click them it teleports you there. After all this I get this error with compiling.. It seems so simple to fix but I don't understand it..
